This lion was saved from canned hunting. A horrific practice where lions  are raised in a small area, pumped full of steroids and growth hormones, and over fed. Only then to be sedated while someone who’s paid $200k shoots them. I have nothing against people who hunt for food they eat, ethically and sustainably. But this is far far from that. Fortunately this king was saved and is now living out his final days in peace. Here he is telling me not to get too close, as he still is a king 🦁
.
